        <h1>Shipping and Delivery Policy</h1>
        <p><strong>Effective Date: May 19, 2025</strong></p>
        <p>At Probioticfy, we are committed to delivering your products promptly and securely. This Shipping and Delivery Policy outlines the details of our shipping process for orders placed on probioticfy.com.</p>

        <h2>1. Shipping Locations</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>We currently ship to addresses within the India.</li>
            <li>International shipping is not available at this time but may be offered in the future. Please check our website for updates.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>2. Order Processing Time</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>Orders are typically processed within 1-2 business days, excluding weekends and Indian govt holidays.</li>
            <li>During peak periods (e.g., holidays or promotions), processing may take up to 3 business days.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>3. Delivery Time</h2>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Standard Shipping:</strong> 3-7 business days within the India after processing.</li>
            <li><strong>Expedited Shipping:</strong> 1-3 business days within the India after processing, if selected at checkout.</li>
            <li>Delivery times are estimates and may vary due to factors like weather, carrier delays, or high order volumes.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>4. Shipping Costs</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>Shipping costs are calculated at checkout based on your location, order weight, and selected shipping method.</li>
            <li>Free standard shipping may be offered for orders meeting a minimum purchase threshold, as indicated at checkout.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>5. Order Tracking</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>Once your order ships, you will receive a confirmation email with a tracking number to monitor your packageâ€™s progress.</li>
            <li>Tracking information may take up to 24 hours to update with the carrier.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>6. Undeliverable Packages</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>If a package is returned to us due to an incorrect address, refusal of delivery, or failure to claim, the customer is responsible for additional shipping costs to resend the order.</li>
            <li>If you choose not to resend, a refund may be issued, minus original shipping costs, per our <a href="/cancellation-refund">Cancellation and Refund Policy</a>.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>7. Delayed or Lost Packages</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>If your order is delayed beyond the estimated delivery time, please contact us at <a href="mailto:contact@probioticfy.com">support@probioticfy.com</a>. We will work with the carrier to resolve the issue.</li>
            <li>For lost packages, we will file a claim with the carrier and offer a replacement or refund once the claim is resolved.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>8. Contact Us</h2>
        <p>For questions or assistance with shipping and delivery, please reach out to:</p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:contact@probioticfy.com">support@probioticfy.com</a></li>
